      "text": [
        " لَا بَأْسَ بِلُبْسِ الْخَاتَمِ لِلْمُحْرِمِ وَ فِي رِوَايَةٍ أُخْرَى لَا يَلْبَسْهُ لِلزِّينَةِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Nasr, from Najeeh, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Al-Hassan<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘There is no problem for the one in <span class=\"iTxt\">Ihraam</span> to wear the ring’. And in another report, (He<sup>asws</sup> said): ‘He should not wear it for the adornment’."
        ]
